headline: G&A Partners Acquires New York-Based CPEO Firm Ethan Allen HR Services, Expanding PEO and HR Outsourcing Capabilities in the Northeast
summary: HOUSTON, January 13, 2026--G&A Partners, a leading professional employer organization (PEO) and human resources outsourcing provider, announced today its acquisition of Ethan Allen HR Services, an Ethan Allen WorkForce Solutions company and prominent IRS-Certified Professional Employer Organization (CPEO) provider based in Poughkeepsie, New York.

headline: The Cigna Group's Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings Release Details
summary: Global health company The Cigna Group (NYSE:CI) will release its fourth quarter 2025 financial results on Thursday, February 5, 2026, and will host a conference call the same day.
